&lt;p&gt;However, you can also go &amp;#39;back&amp;#39; to a previous screen in any lesson - or &amp;#39;fast forward&amp;#39; to a later screen.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To do this, you click and drag the slider in the navigation bar at the bottom right of the screen - you can see it in the image here, highlighted in red.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dragging this slider moves you backwards and forwards through the course, so you can skip to the content you want to see. Try it out!&lt;/p&gt;
